Read me.

Intructions to compile and run Program 2 of Homework 1:

A simple reflex agent with state.

Tested on both stdsun as well as stdlogin.

To compile the program:
========================

Run 'make' in the directory in a Unix environment.
$ make


To run the program:
====================

$ ./solution <path to input file1> <path to input file2>

Example: ./solution hw1-state-belta.txt hw1-state-beltb.txt


To clean up compiled files(i.e delete 'object' files as well as compiled and linked executable):
================================================================================================

$ make clean
